{"tid":2390691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「敗燈」偷取侵侵政續：我先係美國優先！功勞就我攞！","createTime":"2021-02-01T17:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T08:21:31.000Z","uid":219635,"like":2,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2634aa7ae10d31d57fcd24dd035ed940d409a6d5","tid":2390691,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"「蘋果」美國總統拜登上周三就職後，3天已簽署近30項行政命令，從抗疫、經濟、環境等多方面推翻前總統川普的政策，<span class=\"red\">但他周一即將簽署新的行政命令，呼應前總統川普的「買美國貨」（Buy America）美國優先政策，旨在加強政府採購美國製品，以保住美國職位。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n拜登政府的一名官員向記者表示，該命令原意是「增加對製造業及工人的投資，以『重建美好』」，同時促請聯邦機構減少漏洞，避免生產商只在美國生產少部份組件，卻宣稱產品是美國製造。拜登月中公佈的計畫中，已表明會支持製造業，稱將向國會提交「重建美好計劃」（Build Back Better Recovery Plan），重點投資基礎設施、製造業、科研及乾淨能源。<br />\n<br />\n美國受疫情打擊，自去年2月以來流失大約54萬個工廠職位。美聯社引述官員指，行政命令的目標是利用6000億美元（約16.8兆元台幣）聯邦採購開支，刺激本地工廠生產及聘請職位。拜登的命令會修改前朝的「買美國貨」（Buy America）政策，讓承包商更難向聯邦機構賣外國製品；也會改變當中規定，規定更多產品組件必須來自美國工廠；政府也會提高門檻和價格優惠，即政府購買外國產品的價格差異，以保護美國產品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210125/2MY4OJRAJRGDDJ22HOMHFYPVLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210125%2F2MY4OJRAJRGDDJ22HOMHFYPVLU%2F&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=737e9888\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210125%2F2MY4OJRAJRGDDJ22HOMHFYPVLU%2F&h=ca2cd9e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210125/2MY4OJRAJRGDDJ22HOMHFYPVLU/</a>"},{"pid":"cb8562ac0960e45f441d9ad196ce9b946c1f18d9","tid":2390691,"uid":219635,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"又想搶人功勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話侵侵係大壞蛋 害美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">都估到敗燈會因為冇計同冇政續，最後就會抄同沿用返侵侵政策，最後就當自己嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本侵侵政策係好事，對美國有益。</span>"},{"pid":"78fd3822e060c8753939cf4a9e8b20ece48e3660","tid":2390691,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b7f816d8ca21977469b4aa3fa65b7cc08a0a32","tid":2390691,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847a59471e0019c51ae28cdae5da5aaef23ee782","tid":2390691,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f213324f400b13f4fe88f145f00ead3383af6ada","tid":2390691,"uid":173207,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"cb8562ac0960e45f441d9ad196ce9b946c1f18d9","tid":2390691,"uid":219635,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"又想搶人功勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話侵侵係大壞蛋 害美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">都估到敗燈會因為冇計同冇政續，最後就會抄同沿用返侵侵政策，最後就當自己嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本侵侵政策係好事，對美國有益。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"咁都好過佢推翻特朗普嘅政策 累死全世界"},{"pid":"97be335e331a3b3f355d5097bd8c2e4aa119ed21","tid":239069